summary: The unused Fort Dawnguard set piece, DIntRCenter01, fixed and usable.
descriptionHtml:
The piece is unused in Fort Dawnguard, but exists in the set.  Its mesh was incorrect and the piece could not be entered when placed using the Creation Kit.

I have corrected the Z axis of the collision object and added the appropriate material designation; it now works correctly.

To use, unrar the archive into your data/meshes folder.
author: squ3lch
